==Bundles==
Sweet Gem Berry is one of the options for the {{bundle|rare crops||y}}.

==Recipes==
Sweet Gem Berry is not used in any recipes.

==Tailoring==
Sweet Gem Berry is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the {{name|White Turban|class=inline}}.  It can also be used as a red dye in the dye pots, located at [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
Sweet Gem Berry is not used in any [[quests]].

==History==
{{History|1.5|Iridium quality is now possible when using [[Deluxe Fertilizer]].  Bugfix for stages of growth with [[Deluxe Speed-Gro]] + [[Skills#Farming|Agriculturist]]}}

